      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained and reliable vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday utility. The exterior presents beautifully with a vibrant finish, showing only minor road wear such as small stone chips on the hood that are typical for a car of this age. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of major curbing. Inside, the cabin has been kept in impressive condition; the upholstery is clean and free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and all power features\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014operate perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts crisply. It has recently benefited from a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brakes and suspension are in solid working order. This is a turn-key car that has been smoke-free and garage-kept, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without the need for immediate repairs.",
